title: Autocad Civil 3d 2009
description:
Autocad Civil 3D 2009

This is the latest version of the Civil 3D distribution of Autocad released by adobe.  The main focus of this program is varied but includes 3d drafting as well as civil engineering projects. Included is an add-on for water flow in a virtual environment so as to accurately predict certain variables in the scenario.

See the readme for information on unpacking the *.rar format and mounting the discs as well as installation.

I will keep this torrent active for 60 days following the post so that it may adequately be established in the shared environment.
